reviews: I love these sweaters. They fit bigger then you might think I ordered a large but a med would have fit a little better. They have pockets in the front and they are just a nice quality.

I really like it. I finally eliminated my fan in my bedroom I think for good. It has 3 different sounds. Volume control, and a nice night light too. Plus it has 3 time setting options so it will go off long after you fall asleep, which is good for saving power. I put it on my echogear outlet shelf it fits perfect.
Love this little garbage can. Nice design, perfect size for my bathroom.

Love this brush! I think it’s my favourites. It’s shaped different to make it really nice to brush with. It feels like a massage on your scalp as you brush. My hair is shinier and healthier looking since using.
I really like these. Very durable wipes. No gross baby wipe smell, very fresh. Nice packaging

review_title: Good home use nail kit. Cute case
reviews: Love this kit! Love the pretty case and the nail implements inside are of good quality. Everything you need to care for your nails and cuticles. The only thing I don’t use is the nail file, it’s no good.
Nice set, I’m an esthetician that just wanted a cheaper home set to use. Good value for the price. Nice gel colours in this kit. Nicely packaged.
Great quality professional grade comb.
Nice quality hat, with nice stretchy fit.
I love these! Really cute and fun. Pretty good quality and fun for cat lovers
What do you say about a huge peanut butter cup? Yum! Don’t eat all at once!
Nice quality and colours. I love the way they look On my man. He likes them too.
Loved this flavour, never tried before, now one of my favourite! Super fresh, jumbo size and good price. If you love licorice, you’ll love these!

review_title: Great power outage light! I’m getting another one.
reviews: Awesome lantern. I can see us using this for camping, or power outages. Very bright, I advise don’t look at directly. You can manage the amount of light needed by raising or lowering the top, it slides up and down. Super lightweight and portable. Would recommend.
Very nice quality robe. Bought for husband at Christmas. It’s very warm, thick & fluffy. Has pockets & hood. Great for cold days mornings here in Canada.
If you love Marshmallows, you’ll love these. 3 different kinds.
Yummy! So fresh and soft
Nice size, they are bigger than what you might think. Bought for my step son for Christmas stocking stuffer, he’s always loosing keys so I figured a key chain set would help.

Nice looking and very sturdy little shelf. I use the ECHOGEAR Outlet Shelf for multiple items, including my sleep/sound machine for nighttime and my google home mini. I’m going to get a couple more for around the house, it can be used creatively for lots of different things.
This is a great space saver. Especially if your low on drawer space and it looks nice, I want more for my spare rooms now.
Great product it does work beautifully. Just get some practice and your good!
